
/******************Configure Spring without xml*****************/

1. Create a class
2. Add annotations on class
    @Configuration
    @ComponentScan("package to scan")
3. Read Spring Config file
		AnnotationConfigApplicationContext context = 
				new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext(class_name.class);
4. Get the bean from spring container.
		Coach theCoach = context.getBean("class_name with first letter lowercase", (class).class);
